                           In Amharic, written in 1938 A.M. (1945-46 A.D.) in blue ink, in a recent hand.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus/>Fol. 212ra-212rc: Record concerning a reconciliation.<q xml:lang="gez"> 
                              <div style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#xA;justify;line-height:normal"
                                   part="N"
                                   org="uniform"
                                   sample="complete">Fol. 212ra-212rc: በበ፲፱፻፬ ዓመተ፡ ምህረት፡ በዘመነ፡ ዮሃንስ፡ ራስ፡ መኰነን፡ ትግሬ፡ ሲመጡ፡ የኔታ ራሥ፡ መገሻ፡ ሲታሰሩ፡ የኔታ።...</div>
                           </q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           In Amharic, written in 1904 A.M. (= 1911/12 A.D.).
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a4">
                           <locus/> 
                           <div style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#xA;justify;line-height:normal"
                                part="N"
                                org="uniform"
                                sample="complete">Fol. 212rc: Record concerning the renaming of the church.</div>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">  <div style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#xA;justify;line-height:normal"
                                   part="N"
                                   org="uniform"
                                   sample="complete">Fol. 212rc: መዓሊት 29 ቀን 1990 ዓ/ም ብፁእ አቡነ ኤፍሬም ሊቀ ጳጳስ ዘአክሱም ወዘኩሎን አድያማት ትግራይ…</div>
                           </q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           Partly in Amharic, written in 1990 A.M. (1997-98 A.D.), in red and blue pen.
The church, named Säbäya Qǝddǝst Maryam, was renamed as Däbrä Gännät Qǝddǝst Maryam.
The date of 29th Mäggabit 1990 A.M., the stamp and the sign of the Archbishop are placed at the end of the record. 
The record is framed in a square traced by blue pen.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Immediate correction are indicated by a series of dashes and thin lines above the erased words throughout the Ms.: fols. 10ra, 13rb, 27va, 31rc, 33rb.&#xD;
- Interlineal corrections: fols. 24r, 25r, 40va.&#xD;
- Crude drawings of a crosses in the margins, in pencil: fols. 2r, 206v.&#xD;
- Writing excercises: fols. 182v, 212v.</item>
